'''根与芽'''（{{lang-en|Roots & Shoots}}）是一个国际环境组织和自然保育组织，目前根与芽在全球140多个国家都有分布。<ref>{{cite web
 |url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/sierra-club/jane-goodall-sowing-seeds_b_3910289.html
 |title = Jane Goodall: Sowing 'Seeds of Hope'
 |publisher = [[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]
 |access-date = 2020-09-05
 |archive-date = 2017-10-07
 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171007133747/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/sierra-club/jane-goodall-sowing-seeds_b_3910289.html
 |dead-url = no
 }}</ref>

==历史==
1991年[[珍·古道尔|珍·古道尔]]博士在[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]当地学校演讲时发起成立，十二名挑选的当地学生受邀来到她的住处讨论当地环境问题和思索如何改变现状。这十二名学生也被作为组织的初始会员。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Jane Goodall’s Roots & Shoots - The Jane Goodall Institute|url = http://www.janegoodall.org/what-we-do/roots-and-shoots/|website = The Jane Goodall Institute|accessdate = 2015-10-30|language = en|archive-date = 2016-12-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161204185223/http://www.janegoodall.org/what-we-do/roots-and-shoots|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web
 |url = https://www.reuters.com/article/2011/02/19/us-janegoodall-idUSTRE71I3JF20110219
 |title = Jane Goodall toasts 20 years of "Roots and Shoots"
 |publisher = [[路透社|路透社]]
 |access-date = 2020-09-05
 |archive-date = 2015-09-24
 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924151321/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/02/19/us-janegoodall-idUSTRE71I3JF20110219
 |dead-url = yes
 }}</ref>

==分支机构==
至少在全球27个国家或地区有分支机构。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Global Offices - The Jane Goodall Institute|url = http://www.janegoodall.org/who-we-are/contact/global-offices/|website = The Jane Goodall Institute|accessdate = 2015-10-30|language = en|archive-date = 2016-11-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161123033253/http://www.janegoodall.org/who-we-are/contact/global-offices/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

